<view class="page notification-page">
  <custom-navbar eyebrow="消息与提醒" title="订阅消息" />
  <view class="page-content">
    <view class="hero-card">
      <view class="hero-icon">
        <app-icon name="notification" variant="outline" size="54" label="消息通知" />
      </view>
      <view class="hero-copy">
        <text>不错过关键服务进度</text>
        <text>授权由微信管理，拒绝或关闭通知不会影响预约和订单服务。</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="subscription-card">
      <view wx:for="{{items}}" wx:key="key" class="subscription-row">
        <view class="row-copy">
          <view class="row-title">
            <text>{{item.title}}</text>
            <text class="status {{item.status === 'ACCEPTED' ? 'accepted' : item.status === 'BANNED' ? 'banned' : ''}}">{{item.statusText}}</text>
          </view>
          <text>{{item.description}}</text>
        </view>
        <button
          class="row-action tap-feedback"
          disabled="{{busyKey || !item.available}}"
          data-key="{{item.key}}"
          bindtap="enableOne"
        >{{busyKey === item.key ? '处理中' : item.actionText}}</button>
      </view>
    </view>

    <button class="primary-action tap-feedback" disabled="{{busyKey}}" bindtap="enableAll">
      {{busyKey === 'ALL' ? '正在申请授权…' : '开启全部服务通知'}}
    </button>
    <button class="setting-action tap-feedback" bindtap="openWechatSettings">前往微信权限设置</button>

    <view class="notice">
      <text>订阅说明</text>
      <text>一次性订阅通常需要在每次下单或支付后重新获得一次发送机会。若微信授权面板选择保持设置，后续调用可能不再重复弹窗。</text>
      <text>通知仅展示必要的订单状态，不直接展示就诊人、科室详情等敏感医疗信息。</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
